  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Transform 3000 lives with clean water in Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Your support will help acquire an environmentally friendly solar powered water system that will benefit 3000 people including 100 peasant farmers in Namanongo. This will not only help meet the community&apos;s water needs, but also relieve women and girls from the strenuous task of using hand pumps, allowing girls to focus on school and women on income generating activities. Access to water will also secure the health of 1500 and 3500 goats and spur agricultural production and economic activities.</narrative>
  </description>
